data.description: 1 mile from downtown and just 3/4 mi from the coastal trail, this privately fenced 4plex has a 3.875% assumable loan! Move into the freshly remodeled unit with mountain views! Units 2&4 have brand new LVP flooring, solid surface countertops, and fresh paint. Units 1&3 have been updated in recent past. Vinyl windows. 2 large wooden storage sheds included. Units are always easy to rent!#1 - $900 #2 - Vacant for owner occupying buyer! #3 - Freshly Painted for New Tenant 12/1 #4 - $1100  Brand new Smart Maytag washer and dryer are fully maintained by Reliable Commercial Laundry and paid by phone by users. No more need to hassle with quarters or maintain these machines yourself.  Most of the dwellings along this block are single family owner occupied homes. Folks in the cabin across the street have been there since the 70's!
